                    <li><img src="https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcQh_xoMu0dE0bkjz2yoJWIv80Oj9uLAaDmYTNh38drWDAA4itZn2GZJBiOnk7QKEOJ1Xfg&usqp=CAU" alt="Müdür">3- Yüce Honos - 55P</li>
                    <li><img src="https://img.freepik.com/free-vector/beauty-woman-with-green-blouse-character_24877-83554.jpg" alt="Müdür">4- Selena - 55P</li>
                    <li><img src="https://static.vecteezy.com/system/resources/thumbnails/004/899/680/small_2x/beautiful-blonde-woman-with-makeup-avatar-for-a-beauty-salon-illustration-in-the-cartoon-style-vector.jpg" alt="Müdür">5- Aslı - 55P</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="card">
                <h2>Topladığınız Puan</h2>
